# Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy describes how your AdipoMeter app collects, uses, and protects the information provided by users.

## 1. Information Collected

### 1.1 Personal Information
The app requests the following user data to calculate body fat:
- Weight
- Height
- Age
- Gender
- Chest skinfold
- Abdominal skinfold
- Thigh skinfold
- Triceps skinfold
- Subscapular skinfold
- Suprailiac skinfold
- Midaxillary skinfold
- Full Name
- Date of Birth

This information is used **only** for the body fat calculation and is stored **only** locally, but **not** shared with third parties.

### 1.2 Google Analytics
The app uses **Google Analytics** to collect anonymous information about app usage, such as:
- Frequency of use
- Most popular features
- Errors and crashes

This data is used to improve the user experience and app performance. No personally identifiable information is collected or stored by Google Analytics.

### 1.3 Ads
The app displays third-party advertisements to support the maintenance and development of the service. These advertisements may use cookies and similar technologies to personalize the user experience. We have no control over the information collected by third parties for advertising purposes. We recommend that you consult the privacy policies of these advertisers for more information about how they use your data.

## 2. Use of Information

The information provided by the user is used solely to:
- Calculate body fat
- Collect anonymous usage statistics via Google Analytics
- Display third-party advertisements

## 3. Sharing of Information

We **do not share** personal information provided by users with third parties. However, third parties (such as advertisers) may collect anonymized data to personalize the advertising displayed in the application.

## 4. Security

We implement appropriate security measures to protect user data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, please keep in mind that no method of transmission over the Internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.

## 5. Changes to This Policy

This privacy policy may change from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page, and we recommend that you review this policy periodically.

## 6. Contact

If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at apps.sphere.25@gmail.com or visit our GitHub page.
